1.2
log
@* games went off to ports/games/bsdgames
* don't install isakmpd or ctm samples
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: move.c,v 1.6 2002/05/31 04:21:30 pjanzen Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: move.c,v 1.4 1995/04/22 10:08:58 cgd Exp $	*/

